creator: Sennder
descriptionHtml:
Sennder DriverApp helps Carriers & Drivers provide transparency of their service execution while transporting for Sennder. Use the app to track your Sennder orders that have been assigned to you. Use the order details received from your dispatcher and your truck's license plate to start using it.

- Tracking of transports GPS locations with online/offline mode
- Sennder order overview with loading, unloading address

Application is optimized for background GPS tracking and location sync if mobile network is unavailable. The application requires signing up with Sennder as a carrier.
descriptionShort: See all tasks in your schedule and report your progress.

- New app login logic
- Adjusted order overview UI and altered order execution logic and buttons
- New, improved GPS track & trace with support for network unavailability logging
- Added analytics and crashalytics events logging
